<li id="cite_note-7"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7" title="">^</a></b> William Playfair (1807). <a href="http://www.gutenberg.org/catalog/world/readfile?pageno=78&amp;fk_files=195753" class="external text" title="http://www.gutenberg.org/catalog/world/readfile?pageno=78&amp;fk_files=195753" rel="nofollow"><i>An Inquiry into the Permanent Causes of the Decline and Fall of Powerful and Wealthy Nations</i></a>, p. 102.</li>
</ol>
